  "remarks": "Physical description: 5 feet 2 inches; 157,4 cm. Name of father: Ali Muhammad. Mati ur-Rehman is the chief operational commander of Lashkar i Jhangvi (LJ) (QE.L.96.03.). Associated with Harakut-ul Jihad Islami. Reportedly deceased. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 8 November 2022.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 and 1989 Committee on 20 August 2011 (amended 10 May 2012, 17 Oct. 2013, 24 Nov. 2020, 2 February 2023)",
